{"tid":979164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"雷生: 天鑽設計及會所配套吸引年青人，交通亦方便。","createTime":"2019-01-12T13:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T08:56:30.000Z","uid":52010,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8adcb207823d547b1ef2a0f8be3e7baa84679487","tid":979164,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"【大埔天鑽開售】助兒子支付2成首期　雷生：樓價再跌機會唔大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國海外（0688）旗下大埔天鑽今日首推486伙，該盤價格貼近同區二手價，吸引逾7,500張票，超額認購逾14倍。<br />\n<br />\n雷生助準備結婚的兒子付2成首期<br />\n<br />\n助兒子買樓「上車」的雷生表示，已斥580萬元購入2房單位，資助準備結婚、從事金融行業的兒子支付2成首期，約為116萬元。<br />\n<br />\n他認為該盤位置及價錢吸引，比較同區大埔中心二手盤，價格低廉。項目設計及會所配套吸引年青人，交通亦方便。樓價方面，他稱「再跌機會唔大」，現時屬合理水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交通方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7038eda090f9b81a5fb1deba30134d383df11d76","tid":979164,"uid":27961,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"有能力既話幫下自己個仔係好事<br />\n<br />\n第時個仔又幫返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0267241a4d46090ce77f8f4bcd9f732509af64","tid":979164,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"有車實方便"},{"pid":"c7dba162c80a715f37326561c4957285555d4c62","tid":979164,"uid":52010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"揸車不如住大埔村屋算啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dca42c2fc1f926b6e5bbd467ef66306c6179625","tid":979164,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"仲平賣過30年樓嘅大埔中心"},{"pid":"9f9013fdf601b88b3613a21987f158dd9a